Merge pull request #7 from ysak-y/add_unhandled_when_session_start

Add Unhandled function when session start.

Say only first three, no more

If more than three events in a date range, only say the first three, not the actual number of events when the preceding text says first three.

appId never set

The application ID is not set due to case sensitivity, thus the check never occurs. Need to set `alexa.appId = APP_ID` instead of `alexa.AppId = APP_ID` in the `exports.handler`.
Spelling fixes, check for null string, code cleanup
